      },
      {
        title: 'Custom Web Development',
        description:
          'Your website loads in 5 seconds. Your competitor\'s loads in 1 second. Guess who gets the booking? We build conversion-focused websites that load fast, look professional on mobile, and turn visitors into customers.',
        icon: 'tabler:code',
      },
      {
        title: 'PPC Management',
        description:
          'Stop wasting ad spend on clicks that don\'t convert. Our expert PPC management across Google Ads, Meta, Microsoft, LinkedIn, TikTok, and Reddit ensures every dollar contributes to your bottom line with 544% average ROI.',
