      },
      {
        title: 'Marketing Automation',
        description:
          'A lead submits a form at 3 PM. Your team follows up at 9 AM. They\'ve already booked your competitor. Our automation delivers instant SMS + email responses, review requests, and appointment reminders that cut no-shows by 38%.',
        icon: 'tabler:mail-forward',
      },
      {
        title: 'Workflow Automation',
