          'Your customers are on social media—but are you showing up where they scroll? We manage Facebook, Instagram, LinkedIn, TikTok, and Twitter to build engaged communities and drive local leads.',
        icon: 'tabler:brand-facebook',
      },
      {
        title: 'CRM Solutions',
        description:
          'Your customer data is scattered across spreadsheets and sticky notes. We implement HubSpot, Salesforce, Zoho, and custom CRM systems that centralize operations and provide 360-degree customer views.',
        icon: 'tabler:users',
      },
      {
        title: 'E-commerce Solutions',
        description:
          'Whether launching your first online store or scaling to 7 figures, we build Shopify, WooCommerce, and custom e-commerce platforms optimized for checkout conversion and mobile shopping.',
        icon: 'tabler:shopping-cart',
      },
      {
        title: 'Custom Development',
        description:
          'Need a client portal? Custom booking engine? Internal management tool? When off-the-shelf software falls short, we build responsive, scalable web and mobile applications tailored precisely to your business.',
